>>__ load "wordsLib"; Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="words"}; open simpLib;
## `SIZES_ss`

``` hol4
wordsLib.SIZES_ss : ssfrag
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Simplification fragment for words.

The fragment `SIZES_ss` evaluates terms `“dimindex(:'a)”`,
`“dimword(:'a)”`, `“INT_MIN(:'a)”`, and `“FINITE (UNIV : 'a set)”` for
numeric types.

### Example

``` hol4
>>__ load "wordsLib";

>>+ SIMP_CONV (pure_ss++wordsLib.SIZES_ss) [] “dimindex(:32) + INT_MIN(:32) + dimword(:32)”
```

